Package: SpatialScope
Title: Interactive Spatial Transcriptomics Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    c(
      person("Aodong", "Qiu", email = "qiuaodon@pitt.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")),
      person("Mengyao", "Lu", email = "lumenyao@pitt.edu", role = "aut", comment = c("Co-first author"))
    )
Description: An interactive R package with a browser-based interface that enables 
    spatial visualization and analysis directly from processed Seurat objects. Users 
    can interactively select regions of interest (ROI), visualize gene expression 
    patterns, and perform downstream analyses including gene set scoring, spatial 
    clustering, and differential expression analysis.
